{"talk":{"id":2065,"name":"Rose Goslinga: Crop insurance, an idea worth seeding","description":"Across sub-Saharan Africa, small farmers are the bedrock of national and regional economies\u2014unless the weather\u00a0proves\u00a0unpredictable and their crops fail. The solution is insurance, at a vast, continental scale, and at a very low, affordable cost. Rose Goslinga and the Syngenta Foundation for Sustainable Agriculture pioneered an unconventional way to\u00a0give\u00a0farmers whose crops fail early\u00a0a\u00a0second chance at a growing season.","slug":"rose_goslinga_crop_insurance_an_idea_worth_seeding","recorded_at":"2014-06-23 00:00:00","published_at":"2014-08-26 14:48:21","updated_at":"2021-04-09 19:37:08","viewed_count":603896,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":332,"name":"TEDSalon Berlin 2014"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/42a3cd377770922ead215af0ff27bfb6729857d4_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/42a3cd377770922ead215af0ff27bfb6729857d4_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/42a3cd377770922ead215af0ff27bfb6729857d4_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/42a3cd377770922ead215af0ff27bfb6729857d4_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":false,"media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/RoseGoslinga_2014S-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":4964498,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/RoseGoslinga_2014S-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":13704660,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/RoseGoslinga_2014S-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":24324951,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"450k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/RoseGoslinga_2014S-450k.mp4?apikey=c6